Package com.pump.image.gif.block

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GifApplicationExtension
    This block contains application-specific information.
    GifBlock
    A GifBlock is the most fundamental object a GIF can be broken down into.
    GifColorTable  
    GifCommentExtension
    This contains textual information which is not part of the actual graphics in the GIF Data Stream.
    GifExtensionBlock
    This abstract class is just a means to better classify blocks.
    GifGlobalColorTable  
    GifGraphicControlExtension
    This optional block may precede any GifGraphicRenderingBlock.
    GifGraphicRenderingBlock
    This is just a little layer of classification among GifBlocks.
    GifHeaderBlock
    This is the first block in of data in a GIF file.
    GifImageDataBlock
    A block of rasterized image data, encoded via LZW compression.
    GifImageDescriptor
    There must be GifImageDescriptor for each GifImageDataBlock.
    GifInterlace
    This contains some static methods to interlace/uninterlace data according to the GIF definition of interlacing.
    GifLocalColorTable
    This immediately follows a GifImageDescriptor block if its hasLocalColorTable() method returns true.
    GifLogicalScreenDescriptor  
    GifLoopingApplicationExtension
    This is a special block that indicates how many times a GIF should loop.
    GifParser
    This efficiently parses out an InputStream into the appropriate GifBlock's.
    GifPlainTextExtension
    Rarely used in practice, this is a GifGraphicRenderingBlock that displays mono-spaced text.
    GifTrailerBlock
    This 1-byte block identifies the end of a GIF file.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    GifGraphicControlExtension.DisposalMethod
    The disposal methods available for each frame of a gif.
